==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Immeasurable
<hw>Im*meas"ur*a*ble</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Pref.
<ets>im-</ets> not + <ets>measurable</ets>: cf. F.
<ets>measurable</ets>. Cf. <er>Immensurable</er>,
<er>Unmeasurable</er>.]</ety> <def>Incapable of being measured;
indefinitely extensive; illimitable; immensurable; vast.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Of depth <qex>immeasurable</qex>.</q>
<rj><qau>Milton.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Immeasurableness</ent>⟦br⟧
